<div id="smb_timelapse_settings">
    <h4>SMB Timelapse Settings</h4>

    <p>You must provide a hostname, sharename, username, and password to be able to upload rendered timelapses to a SMB Share.</p>


    <form class="form-horizontal" onsubmit="return false;">
        <p>
            <label for="smb_timelapse_hostname"><strong>Hostname</strong></label>
            <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" id="smb_timelapse_hostname" data-bind="value: plugin_settings.smb_timelapse_hostname">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="smb_timelapse_sharename"><strong>Sharename</strong></label>
            <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" id="smb_timelapse_sharename" data-bind="value: plugin_settings.smb_timelapse_sharename">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="smb_timelapse_username"><strong>Username</strong></label>
            <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" id="smb_timelapse_username" data-bind="value: plugin_settings.smb_timelapse_username">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="smb_timelapse_password"><strong>Password</strong></label>
            <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" id="smb_timelapse_password" data-bind="value: plugin_settings.smb_timelapse_password">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="smb_timelapse_delete_after_upload"><strong>Delete After Upload?</strong></label>
            <input class="input-checkbox" type="checkbox" id="smb_timelapse_delete_after_upload" data-bind="checked: plugin_settings.smb_timelapse_delete_after_upload">
        </p>
        <hr/>
        <h5>Custom Events</h5>
        <p>Here you can add custom events that will trigger an upload to SMB.  You need the event name, as well as the payload key that contains the file path.</p>
        <p><b>Note</b>:  The stock timelapse movie done event will ALWAYS trigger an upload, and does not need to be entered here.</p>
        <table class="table table-striped table-hover table-condensed table-hover octolapse-table-list">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Custom Event Name</th>
                <th>Payload Path Key</th>
                <th style="width:55px; text-align:center;">Action</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody data-bind="foreach: plugin_settings.additional_upload_events">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" data-bind="value: $data.event_name">
                </td>
                <td>
                    <input class="input-text input-block-level" type="text" data-bind="attr: {id: 'additional_upload_event_payload_path_key_' + $index() }, value: $data.payload_path_key">
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                    <button class="btn btn-small" type="button" title="Delete Custom Event" data-bind="click: function() { $parent.removeUploadEvent($index());}"><i class="fa fa-trash"></i></button>
                </td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="span12 text-center">
            <button class="btn" type="button" data-bind="click: addUploadEvent"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i> Add Custom Event</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
